{"tid":1384513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求不合作運動，每個星期都要搞","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T06:15:10.000Z","uid":41366,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e467b24fde438e6aa934338a34704f3285da5cd8","tid":1384513,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"眼見咁多次前線手足，勇敢去對抗狗狗同速狗<br />\n每次見到佢地都俾人拘捕<br />\n睇到真係想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來仲要硬食硬膠子彈，過期tear gas<br />\n每個人都賭上自己既前途<br />\n特別係後生果班00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冒着俾人因所謂既暴動罪拘捕<br />\n拉一個少一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒不如為前線提供安全環境去抗爭<br />\n一星期係轉綫站到搞幾次不合作運動<br />\n咁樣先可以格硬將藍C connect 埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋狗狗唔會咁痴線<br />\n係站入邊放tear gas<br />\n咁就可以減低前線手足受傷既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武手足，可以諗諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4851d9733bb3bfff47153198a14ae4c0c4c6eb","tid":1384513,"uid":41366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:04:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況(警黑)<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"7e75ad7947b05337cb522e4cb80f9562ef1e9e8c","tid":1384513,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"提議循序漸進式加碼, <br />\n先係每星期一次, 等香港人適應/留意外界評語, 再決定好唔好一星期多於一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c383b13b04b24b2ce0d41f5c93c3ae8572e0ea","tid":1384513,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e75ad7947b05337cb522e4cb80f9562ef1e9e8c","tid":1384513,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"提議循序漸進式加碼, <br />\n先係每星期一次, 等香港人適應/留意外界評語, 再決定好唔好一星期多於一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:19:34.000Z","msg":"做乜都俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n倒不如揀個比較安全既方法，<br />\n保障前線手足安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b44f2927e4e92601cdeddd73402b94a2f6a32d9","tid":1384513,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:30:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60d60ad6ee82b06673b7cf86e4bc727ecd0d5107","tid":1384513,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n自推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMXA6CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: